text: Fredrik Hultén (9 November 1966 - 13 June 1997) was a Swedish rower. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:1997 deaths Category:Swedish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Sweden Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lund
